  "text": "On the other hand, HSPs including, HSP40, 70, and 90, play a role in the assembly and nuclear import of influenza virus RNA polymerase, in stimulating influenza virus activity that mediates apoptosis, and in regulating the activity of dsRNA dependent protein kinase that inhibits innate immune responses [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
